## How This Works

After each GAMET review, update this log:
1. What scored well (A) → add to "What Works"
2. What scored poorly (C or below) → add to "Recurring Issues"
3. New patterns discovered → add to "Patterns"

This log is read by Impact Analysis, so learnings from past work inform future work.

